OL,5, A Spanish court has cleared a British  
OL,6, man of public disorder, after he joked 
OL,7, to friends about blowing up a flight   
OL,8, from London Gatwick to Menorca.        
OL,10,FAditya Verma admitted he told friends  
OL,11,Fin July 2022: "On my way to blow up the
OL,12,Fplane. I'm a member of the Taliban."   
OL,14,FBut he said he had made the joke in a  
OL,15,Fprivate Snapchat group and never       
OL,16,Fintended to "cause public distress".   
OL,18,FA judge in Madrid ruled that "no       
OL,19,Fexplosive ... was found that would lead
OL,20,Fone to believe it was a real threat".  
